net.sf.gogui.game
Class GameTree

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.gogui.game.GameTree
All Implemented Interfaces:
ConstGameTree
public class GameTree
extends java.lang.Object
implements ConstGameTree

Game tree. Note that the tree can have different GameInfo objects for different subtrees to allow the representation of trees loaded from SGF. Creating trees with multiple GameInfo objects is not not actively supported in GoGui, because they cannot be saved in (Jago's) XML format.
